= XML Index =
A nice looking an easily customizable directory index for your mailserver
maintenance domain.

== installation ==
Copy index.xml and oma_tabular.xsl to the root directory of your domain,
with Openmailadmin being installed at /openmailadmin. (Else you will have to
alter paths by hand.)

== known bugs ==
Width of tables is not preserved under Firefox.

